headline: Q3 Earnings Highs And Lows: Arthur J. Gallagher (NYSE:AJG) Vs The Rest Of The Insurance Brokers Stocks
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how insurance brokers stocks fared in Q3, starting with Arthur J. Gallagher (NYSE:AJG).
